data.title: Claremont McKenna College
data.meta_description: Claremont McKenna College, one of the nationâ€™s top liberal arts colleges, prepares students to make a difference. The College educates students for thoughtful and productive lives and roles of responsible leadership through its strong, real-world mission. Admission to the College is need-blind
